full_title: Never Lose Me by Flo Milli
title: Never Lose Me

description.plain:
“Never Lose Me” is a track by Flo Milli featured on her highly anticipated second studio album Fine Ho, Stay.

A viral hit, “Never Lose Me” is not only an anthem for the ladies, but an affirmation of Flo’s self-worth, confidence and loyalty.
